<h3 class="md:text-lg">Trans-Saharan Challenges: Smuggling, Terrorism, and the Struggle for a State (Part 1)</h3>
<div class="category-date flex justify-between md:hidden">
<span class="category text-xxs uppercase"></span>
<span class="date text-xxs uppercase">Jan 17</span>
</div>
</div>
</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="news-box md:px-2 md:w-1/3">
